Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley

288
00:22:57,690 --> 00:23:00,350
In and around the lake

289
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:05,510
Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there

290
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:12,270
One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you

291
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:18,700
Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too

292
00:23:21,390 --> 00:23:27,000
Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be there with you

293
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:31,100
俺の祖父に起こった悲劇を
在我祖父身上发生的悲剧

294
00:23:31,100 --> 00:23:34,180
ならばテメエは この鳩にさえ勝てやしねぇぜ
那你就连这只鸽子都打不赢

295
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:36,380
紫外線の照射量をもっと多くしろ
增加紫外线的照射量

296
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:39,510
目覚めたまえ 我が主たちよ
醒来吧 我的主人们

297
